description:
Peacemaker Season 2 kicks off! Join Frankey Smith, Tyler Coates, and Coy Jandreau as they break down Episodes 1 & 2—covering major plot twists, character arcs, and those unforgettable dance sequences. Plus, an exclusive interview with choreographer Charissa Barton, the creative mind behind Peacemaker’s iconic intros. Get behind-the-scenes secrets, future teases, and DC Universe updates! Subscribe for new episodes every other Friday.

description:
Join James Gunn with co-hosts Steve Agee (John Economos) and Jennifer Holland (Emilia Harcourt) in the official Peacemaker podcast as they dive deep into Season 2, Episode 2, “A Man Is Only As Good As His Bird” of Peacemaker. Along with special guest Freddie Stroma (Vigilante/Adrian Chase), the gang shares exclusive behind-the-scenes stories, from character arcs and emotional fallout to Greg Mottola’s directorial style and new cast additions like Tim Meadows as Langston Fleury.
